_sText:
Gg_illumination

Made by MachINE

This is my first gungame map and first released map for that matter. The theme is futuristic. I have used mostly standard textures. There is enviromental lighting, volumetric fog, ambient sounds, and a 2d skybox made by Karatekafer.

The max players is 42.

Enjoy,

MachINE

<hr>


Visit www.notetwo.co.uk and forums.solidsurf.info, great mapping communities!
